### Get All Offers
GET {{OffersApi_HostAddress}}/api/offers?page=1&pageSize=10

### Get Offers by Seller
GET {{OffersApi_HostAddress}}/api/offers?sellerId=a1b2c3d4-e5f6-7890-abcd-ef1234567890&page=1&pageSize=10

### Get Offers by Status
GET {{OffersApi_HostAddress}}/api/offers?status=Active&page=1&pageSize=10

### Get Offer by ID (replace with actual ID)
GET {{OffersApi_HostAddress}}/api/offers/{{offerId}}

### Update Offer (replace with actual ID)
PUT {{OffersApi_HostAddress}}/api/offers/{{offerId}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "offerAmount": 27000.00,
  "location": {
    "city": "San Jose",
    "state": "CA",
    "zipCode": "95101",
    "country": "USA"
  }
}

### Cancel Offer (replace with actual ID)
POST {{OffersApi_HostAddress}}/api/offers/{{offerId}}/cancel

